简体中文：
Win7Games语言精简版是基于Windows 7操作系统中的小游戏精简而成，并修改为仅使用英文（en_US）和简体中文（zh_CN）语言的版本。本项目旨在提高这些小游戏在Linux下的兼容性，使其能够在Wine环境下运行。
请注意，原小游戏是Windows 7操作系统的一部分，其版权属于微软公司。本项目对原小游戏进行了调整和优化，并没有改变其核心玩法或内容。
本项目不拥有任何Windows 7内置小游戏的版权。所有小游戏的内容和原始版权仍然属于微软公司。
本项目不对用户使用、修改或分发这些小游戏的行为负责。用户应自行确保其使用行为符合相关法律法规。
本项目不提供任何形式的明示或暗示保证，包括但不限于适销性、特定用途适用性和非侵权性。任何因使用本项目而引起的损失或损害，项目开发者不承担任何责任。
English:
Win7Games Language Lite is a version based on the mini games in the Windows 7 operating system, modified to only use English (en-US) and Simplified Chinese (zh_CN) languages. This project aims to improve the compatibility of these mini games on Linux, enabling them to run in the Wine environment.
Please note that the original mini game is part of the Windows 7 operating system and its copyright belongs to Microsoft Corporation. This project has made adjustments and optimizations to the original mini game, without changing its core gameplay or content.
This project does not own the copyright of any built-in mini games in Windows 7. All content and original copyrights of the mini games still belong to Microsoft Corporation.
This project is not responsible for the user's use, modification, or distribution of these mini games. Users should ensure that their usage behavior complies with relevant laws and regulations.
This project does not provide any form of express or implied warranty, including but not limited to merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non infringement. The project developer shall not be liable for any loss or damage caused by the use of this project.